added.title: Paint That a Shame
added.description: Leshawna creates a paint balloon fight to decide who gets to come with her to an amusement park.

added.title: Snots Landing
added.description: Beth gets Courtney's diorama furniture stuck up her nose and Courtney needs it back before the diorama contest judge arrives.

added.title: Know it All
added.description: Courtney must go all day without correcting her friends which is hard because they do everything wrong!

added.title: A Licking Time Bomb
added.description: Owen and Noah unwittingly become cookie moguls and must hide the secret ingredient, which is Owen's spit from licking the sprinkles off the cookies.

added.title: From Badge to Worse
added.description: In order to earn her final Girl Campers badge Courtney must earn Gwen's friendship.

added.title: Ace of Squares
added.description: Craig vows to make the game of Four Square fun again by challenging its most dominant player!

added.title: Doorway to Helen
added.description: Craig makes a long distance connection with a kid that loves the creek as much as he does.

added.title: The Last Kid in the Creek
added.description: A terrible curse leaves Craig as the only kid in the creek.

added.title: The Climb
added.description: Craig's phone gets stuck in Mt. Sycamore, the tallest tree in the creek!

added.title: Big Pinchy
added.description: JP leads his friends on a voyage to find the biggest crayfish in the creek.

added.title: Hot Sauce
added.description: A quest for their favorite hot sauce causes the Bears to get involved with a sting operation.

added.title: Mom App
added.description: Hoping to finally get the mom-experience, the Bears use an app that'll bring a mom right to their door.

added.title: The Limo
added.description: To help distract Panda from his girl problems, Grizz and Ice Bear treat him to a ride in a limo.

added.title: More Everyone's Tube
added.description: Through another video browsing session online, we get more videos uploaded by the Bears and their friends.

added.title: Money Man
added.description: The Bears help Chloe present her project for a college science contest. But Chloe's rival makes things difficult.

added.title: Pool Duel
added.description: Unikitty and the gang are having a great time at the public pool, until they try to get Puppycorn to swim in the deep end with them. Puppycorn is terrified of the deep end. Now Unikitty and the gang must get him over his fear, so he can have maximum pool fun. Meanwhile, Master Frown and Brock are hatching a plan to ruin everyone's fun, by pulling the pool's plug.

added.title: Tooth Trouble
added.description: Puppycorn loses his first tooth and Unikitty's excited for her little bro, now he​ ​gets a visit from​ ​the​ ​legendary Tooth Fairy!​ ​But when the Tooth Fairy is a no-show, Unikitty and her friends take on the mantle and responsibilities. But will they play too fast and loose with loose teeth and hit a raw nerve?

added.title: This Spells Disaster
added.description: The gang is planning a surprise for Puppycorn, so they spell things out when talking so he won't find out. Desperate to know what they're saying, Puppycorn finds a magic book that he thinks will help him learn to spell, but unbeknownst to him, it's teaching him how to cast spells! Will Puppycorn realize that knowledge is power and some secrets are kept for a reason?

added.title: Roadtrip Ruckus
added.description: Richard has decided to take Unikitty and the gang for a pleasant and relaxing 10 hour road trip. At first everyone is against the trip, but they soon start to have fun. Unfortunately, their idea of fun is not Richard's.  He soon begins to give in to his inner road-rage. To make matters worse they are being chased by a killer semi-truck, and their car has been invaded by weird bug hitchhiker.  Will Richard loose it, or will the trip be a great success?

added.title: Memory Amok
added.description: When Puppycorn witnesses Unikitty do the most embarrassing thing ever, he vows he will never forget it. Desperate, Unikitty uses Dr. Fox's memory machine to erase Puppycorn's memory of the embarrassing event. In the process, Unikitty accidentally releases all of Puppycorn's memories. Now she and the gang must scramble to capture all the scampering memories, or Puppycorn will forget his life.

added.title: Cosmic Bupkiss
added.description: A storm blocks Oscar and Hedgehog's one chance to see a comet.

added.title: Radio Silence
added.description: Oscar must get Hedgehog a special sandwich in order to save their friendship.

added.title: Director's Cut
added.description: Oscar receives a camcorder from his parents and sets out to prove to them the magic on the island is real.

added.title: I Heart Heartforde
added.description: Oscar, hedgehog and the other campers are excited to take a trip to the non-magical town of Heartforde.

added.title: Salsa Picante
added.description: La búsqueda de su salsa picante favorita hace que los Osos se involucren en una operación de picadura.

added.title: Mama a la Orden
added.description: Con el deseo de tener la experiencia de una madre, los osos usan una aplicación que les traerá una madre a la puerta de sus casas.

added.title: La Limosna
added.description: Para ayudar a Panda a distraerse de sus problemas románticos, Pardo y Polar le regalan un paseo en limosina.

added.title: Problemas Dentales
added.description: A Puppycorn se le cae su primer diente, y Unikitty está emocionada por su hermanito, ique ahora recibirá la visita de la legendaria Hada de los Dientes! Pero cuando el Hada de los Dientes no aparece, Unikitty y sus amigos asumen la responsabilidad. ¿Acaso se meterán demasiado rápido y con demasiada soltura con los dientes sueltos y tocarán un nervio sensible?

added.title: Letras Desastrosas
added.description: La pandilla está planeando una sorpresa para Puppycorn, así que deletrean las cosas cuando hablan para que él no se entere. Desesperado por saber lo que dicen, Puppycorn encuentra un libro mágico que cree que lo ayudará a aprender a deletrear, ipero sin saberlo, el libro le enseña a lanzar hechizos! ¿Se dará cuenta Puppycorn de que el conocimiento es poder, y de que algunos secretos se guardan por una razón?

added.title: Viaje en Carretera
added.description: Richard decidió llevar a Unikitty y a la banda a un agradable y relajante viaje de 10 horas por la carretera. Al principio todo el mundo está en contra del viaje, pero pronto empiezan a divertirse. Por desgracia, su idea de diversión no es la de Richard. Pronto, el conductor comienza a sucumbir ante su furia interior al volante. Para colmo de males, los persigue un semirremolque asesino, y su coche ha sido invadido por un extraño autoestopista. ¿Richard perderá la razón o el viaje será un gran éxito?

added.title: Guerra de Bromas
added.description: Cuando Master Frown comienza una guerra de bromas con el Unireino, los amigos están listos para contraatacar. Pero Unikitty no entiende bien las bromas, y piensa que tienen demasiada maldad. ¿Pueden los amigos ayudar a Unikitty a comprender una buena broma y ganar la guerra contra Frown? ¿O se verán obligados a sufrir sus bromas sin represalias y admitir la derrota?

added.title: Pintura dolorosa
added.description: Leshawna inventa una pelea con globos llenos de pintura para ver quién va al parque de diversiones con ella.

added.title: Aterrizaje mocoso
added.description: A Beth se le atascan los muebles del diorama de Courtney en la nariz y Courtney tiene que recuperarlos antes de que llegue el juez del concurso de dioramas.

added.title: Sabelotodo
added.description: Courtney debe pasar todo el día sin corregir a sus amigos, y eso es difícil porque lo hacen todo mal.

added.title: Una bomba para lamer
added.description: Sin querer, Owen y Noah se convierten en magnates de las galletas y deben ocultar el ingrediente secreto, que es la saliva que deja Owen al lamerse las chispas.

added.title: De la insignia al peor
added.description: Para ganarse la última insignia que le falta de las Chicas Exploradoras, Courtney debe ganarse la amistad de Gwen.
